==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nuthook
<hw>Nut"hook`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A hook
at the end of a pole to pull down boughs for gathering the
nuts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A thief who steals by means of a hook; also, a
bailiff who hooks or seizes malefactors.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nutjobber</ent>⟦br⟧
